NOTE ON TERMINOLOGY DATA:

This software is designed to work with clinical terminology data from various
sources. The MIT license above applies to the software code only.

Terminology data has separate licensing requirements:

- SNOMED-CT: Requires a UMLS license. See SNOMED_LICENSE.md for details.
- LOINC: Free registration required at loinc.org.
- ICD-10-CM: Public domain (CDC/CMS).
- CDT: Copyright ADA, used under fair use for interoperability.
- RxNorm: Public domain (NLM/NIH).

Users are responsible for ensuring they have appropriate licenses for any
terminology data they load into the system.